{"tha-ap287:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap287:0.2":"Pannadayakavagga ","tha-ap287:0.3":"Maghavapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap287:1.1":"“Nammadanadiya tire, ","tha-ap287:1.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap287:1.3":"Samadhim so samapanno, ","tha-ap287:1.4":"vippasanno anavilo. ","tha-ap287:2.1":"Disva pasannasumano, ","tha-ap287:2.2":"sambuddham aparajitam; ","tha-ap287:2.3":"Taham maghavapupphena, ","tha-ap287:2.4":"sayambhum pujayim tada. ","tha-ap287:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap287:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap287:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap287:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap287:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap287:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap287:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap287:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma maghavapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap287:6.1":"Maghavapupphiyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}